                amazing Classic Frank. For a 100% Frank experience, go with this Stein.</item>
        <item>This Belgian Red beer follows the tradition of slightly soured red ale. Steins Red goes
                great solo or accompanied by a tasty Frank.</item>
        <item>The Frank ‘N’ Steins porter has been a staple brand at our restaurant. This dark Stein
